Guided Tour

Join a one hour guided tour of the Museum on Saturdays, or book a tour in advance for any visit for a group.

Saturday tours
On Saturdays there is a drop-in one-hour introductory tour of the Museum with a Cambridge Badge Guide at 14.30. Meet at the Courtyard Entrance at least 10 minutes in advance to join the tour. Your place on this tour can also be booked in advance through the Cambridge Visitor Information Centre, tel. 01223 791501, email: tours@visitcambridge.org.
Â£6 per person.

Group tours
Guided tours for private groups can be booked in advance of your visit. Contact Cambridge Visitor Information Centre, tel. 01223 791501, email: tours@visitcambridge.org.